{"tid":2214489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應潘曉穎父母公開信促陳同佳投案　曾稱自己非「陳同佳代言人」　管浩鳴：下星期與陳見面後回覆","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:14:28.000Z","uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14673833e21a41a980a2d25e29d5988fb8cb2a2e","tid":2214489,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"2018 年 2 月涉嫌在台灣殺害潘曉穎的陳同佳，去年 10 月在港因四項洗黑錢罪刑滿出獄後，稱願意到台灣自首，但至今未成行，一直居住在警方安排的「安全屋」；潘曉穎母親日前接受《立場新聞》獨家專訪，要求陳同佳盡快兌現承諾、赴台投案；潘曉穎父母今日（23 日）再透過《立場》對陳同佳發公開信，指香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴已表示自己不是其「代言人」，所以要求陳同佳親自回應何時赴台，對此，管浩鳴回應傳媒查詢時稱，「等我下星期和同佳見面後再回覆大家。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%BD%98%E6%9B%89%E7%A9%8E%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1%E4%BF%83%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E6%8A%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%9D%9E-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA-%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4-%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E8%88%87%E9%99%B3%E8%A6%8B%E9%9D%A2%E5%BE%8C%E5%9B%9E%E8%A6%86/?fbclid=IwAR3zs4_2DvfpDf1ZUcSE9npvCbxVlpZjr3zofXljbSez0uTKjmtAS9hKgGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%25BD%2598%25E6%259B%2589%25E7%25A9%258E%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E9%259D%259E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25A6%2586%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3zs4_2DvfpDf1ZUcSE9npvCbxVlpZjr3zofXljbSez0uTKjmtAS9hKgGM&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9ryOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=3f1beac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=